    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. Perfect for anyone looking for something reliable without breaking the bank. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
