      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances daily utility with pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though light stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch on the rear quarter panel are present upon close inspection\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, showing only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has a documented service history, including a recent oil change, new air filters, and a brake system flush performed within the last 3,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the car tracks straight and true at highway speeds. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for a new owner who appreciates a car that has been looked after both mechanically and cosmetically.",
